        <div xml:id="OTP34743139">
        <fw type="pageNum">Page 1</fw>
          <p corresp='TTP34743139P0' xml:id='OTP34743139P0'><b><hi rend='italic'>OFFICE OF</hi></b><lb/>
<b><rs ref='#S32067465'>J. J. Anderson</rs>,</b><lb/>
<rs ref='#S95578'>SHERIFF</rs> AND <rs ref='#S91163'>TAX COLLECTOR</rs>,<lb/>
<b>UNION COUNTY, MISS.</b>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34743139P1' xml:id='OTP34743139P1'><hi rend='italic'><rs ref='#S54037'>New Albany</rs>,</hi> Copy <hi rend='italic'>187</hi>[gap]
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34743139P2' xml:id='OTP34743139P2'>The State of Mississippi<lb/>
Union County<lb/>
To the Sheriff of said<lb/>
County<lb/>
<hr/>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34743139P3' xml:id='OTP34743139P3'>We recommend you to take the Body of <rs ref='#S32103602'>Jno Warren</rs> of to be found in your county and him safely keep so that you have his body before the Honerable <rs ref='#S70054'>circuit court</rs> of union county in sam state to be held at the court House thereof in the Town of New Albany in the Third monday of Feburay AD 1879 then and there to answer unto the State of Miss in <rs ref='#S32074731'>charge</rs> of <rs ref='#S63926'>murder</rs> by infermation filed in said court in the Aug Term A. D. 1878 thereof Given under my hand &amp; pen This 28<add place='above'>th</add> day of Aug 1878
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34743139P4' xml:id='OTP34743139P4'><rs ref='#S32174466'>N. P. Smith</rs><lb/>
Clerk
</p>


        </div>
        <pb xml:id="F34743140" n="2" facs="https://cdm17313.contentdm.oclc.org/iiif/2/mdah:45771/full/full/0/default.jpg"/>
