          <p corresp='TTP34743140P0' xml:id='OTP34743140P0'>J. J. Anderson
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34743140P1' xml:id='OTP34743140P1'>Wants an additional reward for John Warren
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34743140P2' xml:id='OTP34743140P2'>Negative answer<lb/>
Oct 3<add place='above'><hi rend='underline'>d</hi></add> 1878
</p>

<p corresp='TTP34743140P3' xml:id='OTP34743140P3'>A True Copy of the <rs ref='#S95194'>indictment</rs>
</p>


